N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 22.42 - Minimum class i price

State Regulations

Minimum class I price. The minimum class I price per
hundredweight of pool milk shall be the basic formula price for the second
preceding month plus $2.42. Notes
